Workshops

We run 4 workshop series with the support of the data consultants. Each series consists of several workshops over the term, offered on a weekly basis. Students can enroll in any or all of the series listings.

We also encourage students to sign up for complementary workshops when possible. To this end, 6 students registered for both Learning R and Fundamentals, 11 for Fundamentals and Fitting Models, 4 for Learning R and Fitting Models, and 3 for all 3 series.

The series on Bayesian statistics was developped this academic year.

Learning R was offered in W1, the remaining workshops were offered in W2.
